Hello,

This email confirms the details of your upcoming visit. Please review the information below and contact us if anything needs to be corrected.

Name: {{31.result.name}}
Email: {{31.result.email}}
Phone Number: {{31.result.phoneNumber}}
Date: {{formatDate(29.data.startedAt; "YYYY-MM-DD hh:mm A")}}
Urgency: {{31.result.urgency}} out of 10
Estimated Visit Time: {{31.result.visitTime}}
Summary: {{31.result.summary}}

If any of the information above is incorrect or you need to update your appointment, please reply to this email or call our office. Thank you.

Other Medical Notes:
{{31.result.medicalNotes}}

Sincerely,
AIDE Team

